quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  63,9,"O you who believe! do not let your wealth and your children divert you from the remembrance of Allah, and whoever does that, then those are the persons at loss"
  63,10,"And spend from that which We have provided you, before death comes to one of you (and) then he says, “My Fosterer! why do you not postpone (this) for me till a near term so that I could give charity and become one of the righteous?”"
  63,11,"And Allah never postpones (death for) any soul when its term comes (to an end), and Allah is informed of that which you do"